		//		A mixin that implements the base functionality for `dijit/form/ComboBox`/`dijit/form/FilteringSelect`
		// description:
		//		All widgets that mix in dijit/form/_AutoCompleterMixin must extend `dijit/form/_FormValueWidget`.
